Snowball stemming library collection for PHP
============================================

The PHP stemmer has been largely modified from the JavaScript library with 
base-stemmer.php being translated from base-stemmer.js with virtually no 
knowledge of the underlying algorithm.

Likewise, the compiler code in generator_php.c was copied mostly from 
generator_js.c with some ideas taken from the generator_python.c, as noted in 
the source code.


How to use library
------------------

Once Snowball is compiled, generate your langague stemmer:

.. code-block:: bash

    ./snowball algorithms/english.sbl -php -o php/en-stemmer


Then use it from PHP as follows:

.. code-block:: php

    require __DIR__.'/en-stemmer.php';
    $stemmer = new SnowballEnStemmer;
    $word = 'Compiled';
    $stem = $stemmer->stemWord($word);
    printf("%s => %s\n", $word, $stem );

	// Compiled => Compil
